absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-between p-3 sm:p-4 z-10"><div><h3 class="text-white text-base sm:text-[16px] md:text-[18px] font-extrabold leading-tight mt-4 sm:mt-8" style="font-family:exo-2, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em">AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION</h3><p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-lg font-light leading-snug mt-2 sm:mt-3 line-clamp-4">Transmission that automatically shifts gears without driver intervention, offering convenience, especially in urban driving.</p></div></div></div><div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg w-full h-[200px] md:h-[300px] lg:h-[270px] bg-black/50"><img alt="CONTINUOUSLY VARIABLE TRANSMISSION (CVT)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover opacity-60" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Fcvt.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-between p-3 sm:p-4 z-10"><div><h3 class="text-white text-base sm:text-[16px] md:text-[18px] font-extrabold leading-tight mt-4 sm:mt-8" style="font-family:exo-2, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em">CONTINUOUSLY VARIABLE TRANSMISSION (CVT)</h3><p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-lg font-light leading-snug mt-2 sm:mt-3 line-clamp-4">Utilizes belts or chains to smoothly change the gear ratio, ensuring smooth transitions and fuel efficiency.</p></div></div></div><div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg w-full h-[200px] md:h-[300px] lg:h-[270px] bg-black/50"><img alt="AUTOMATED MANUAL TRANSMISSION (AMT)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover opacity-60" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Ftransmission%2Fimages%2Famt.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/><div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-between p-3 sm:p-4 z-10"><div><h3 class="text-white text-base sm:text-[16px] md:text-[18px] font-extrabold leading-tight mt-4 sm:mt-8" style="font-family:exo-2, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em">AUTOMATED MANUAL TRANSMISSION (AMT)</h3><p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-lg font-light leading-snug mt-2 sm:mt-3 line-clamp-4">Automated manual transmission with manual mode, offering auto convenience and manual control.</p></div></div></div><div class="relative flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg w-full h-[200px] md:h-[300px] lg:h-[270px] bg-black/50"><img alt="ELECTRIC TRANSMISSION" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover opacity-60" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top